New song dropping this coming Friday #heartland w @cowboytroyglobal co-written and produced by @brettboyett proud of this amazing collaboration 🙏🏼

Heartland is a gritty, stomp-influenced, country-rock song with a message of American values. It sings about our idea of a down-home American dream girl raised up and home grown in The Heartland as the song states in the bridge. With its Americana sounding intro it grows into a driving Lynard Skynard feeling song praising down-home roots and the blood sweat, and tears (struggle) of blue collar life, while highlighting the immense contributions of American women.
